article.description: — Isaiah Moses had 22 points in UC Riverside's 74-68 win over Green Bay on Tuesday night.
article.headline: UC Riverside wins 74-68 over Green Bay
article.linkText: UC Riverside wins 74-68 over Green Bay
article.story: BOZEMAN, Mont. -- — Isaiah Moses had 22 points in UC Riverside's 74-68 win over Green Bay on Tuesday night. Moses also contributed six assists for the Highlanders (2-3). Vladimer Salaridze scored 14 points, going 7 of 9 from the field. Barrington Hargress shot 4 for 8, including 1 for 3 from beyond the arc to finish with nine points. Noah Reynolds led the Phoenix (2-3) in scoring, finishing with 19 points and eight assists. Rich Byhre added 14 points for Green Bay. David Douglas Jr. also had 12 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
